---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-24 border-t border-line/70 bg-surface/50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between">
      <div class="max-w-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
          <span class="grid h-8 w-8 place-items-center rounded-lg bg-primary-600 font-display text-sm font-bold text-white" aria-hidden="true">AI</span>
          <span class="font-display text-base font-bold text-ink">디지털 교육자료 수업 지원센터</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
          대구광역시교육청 AI 디지털교과서(AIDT) 수업 활용을 돕는
          도움자료·문의 지원 창구입니다.
        </p>
      </div>

      <nav aria-label="바닥글 메뉴" class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-10 gap-y-2 text-sm">
        <a class="text-muted transition-colors hover:text-primary-700" href="/index">안내</a>
        <a class="text-muted transition-colors hover:text-primary-700" href="/index/feedback">출판사 지원</a>
        <a class="text-muted transition-colors hover:text-primary-700" href="/class">수업이야기</a>
        <a class="text-muted transition-colors hover:text-primary-700" href="/study">스스로 학습</a>
        <a class="text-muted transition-colors hover:text-primary-700" href="/index/faq">자주 묻는 질문</a>
        <a class="text-muted transition-colors hover:text-primary-700" href="/contact">문의·장애 지원</a>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 border-t border-line/70 pt-6 text-xs text-muted">
      © {year} 대구광역시교육청 · AI·디지털 교육자료 수업 지원센터
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
